##### ULMS

The differential expression analysis is done without covariate.

```{r resultsDeseq2Vnn1HighVsLowTcgaSarcULMSKnitPostDeseq2Template, cache=FALSE, results="asis"}
source("loadEnv.R")

smi <- "out/r/compute_deseq2/VNN1/HighVsLowTcgaSarcULMS_ddss.rds"
linkSmiToRmdAndBookDir(smi)
ddss <- readRDS(smi)

smi <- "out/r/compute_deseq2/VNN1/HighVsLowTcgaSarcULMS_ddssr.rds"
linkSmiToRmdAndBookDir(smi)
ddssr <- readRDS(smi)

knitPostDeseq2Template(
  d = ddss,
  r = ddssr
)
```
